  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You snap your hands forward in a sudden motion. A gust of cold air flows through your throat and out into the air as you cry out an old primordial battle cry in the auran dialect. The air before you whips and lashes at all creatures and objects before you as they are thrown around.</em></p><p><strong>Strength Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 3d6 bludgeoning]] damage and [[/damage 3d6 slashing]] damage*. Targets are all moved up to 15 ft. either closer or further away from you.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 bludgeoning]] and [[/damage 1d6 slashing]] damage for each spell level above 4th.</p>",
      "chat": "<p><strong>Strength Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 3d6 bludgeoning]] damage and [[/damage 3d6 slashing]] damage*. Targets are all moved up to 15 ft. either closer or further away from you.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 bludgeoning]] and [[/damage 1d6 slashing]] damage for each spell level above 4th.</p>"
